data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Nicely maintained 3-bedroom, 2-bath, 2 car garage residence is a haven of comfort and style. New Roof to be added.  As you approach, the captivating curb appeal beckons you inside.  Step through the front door and be greeted by the grandeur of high ceilings in the living room and dining area, creating an open and airy ambiance that immediately feels like home. The spacious and bright living room provides a welcoming space for relaxation and gatherings, while the dining area, with its lofty ceiling, is perfect for delightful meals with friends and family.  Sliders out to the lanai open the home up to the outside.  The kitchen offers an abundance of countertop space for meal preparation, cooking, and entertaining. The thoughtful design ensures that every culinary adventure is a breeze, whether you're creating a family feast or experimenting with new recipes. The master bedroom is a private retreat, featuring a convenient his-and-her sink setup that adds a touch of luxury and efficiency. The walk-in shower in the master bath adds another layer of comfort and convenience to this exquisite space. The additional bedrooms along with full bath are versatile, perfect for family members, guests, or a home office. The property's exterior is equally impressive. The meticulously maintained fenced yard provides a secure space, as well as an inviting area for outdoor activities and gatherings. The curb appeal of this home is a testament to the care and attention given to its maintenance, making it a standout in the neighborhood. Situated in a fantastic area, this home offers the best of both worlds: a tranquil and well-maintained community while being conveniently located to local amenities, schools, parks, and shopping. Commuting is a breeze with easy access to major highways and public transportation, making this property an ideal choice for anyone looking for a great location.
